&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you passionate about education and training, do you have excellent people skills, are you confident enough to present in front of senior clinical and support staff?  If so, we are looking for a highly motivated, innovative and experienced clinician to join the Southern Health Resuscitation Team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role will include the delivery of and evaluation of:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;•           Basic Life Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;•           Immediate Life Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;•           Clinical scenario training&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;In addition, the post holder will be expected to assist and support the design, delivery and evaluation of courses, as well as support the Lead Resuscitation Officer in audit, simulations and other project work as it arises. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will report to the Lead Resuscitation Officer. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You must hold a Professional Registration and have teaching experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are interested in applying for this permanent post, please read the attached Job Description and contact us should you require an informal chat or visit.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;To obtain further information contact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hayley Stockford, Resuscitation Officer Mobile: 07917 277 093&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
